QUEST CONTROLS:
DPAD UP - RUN
R1 - STOP
R1 + LEFT OR RIGHT - STANDING TURN
R1 + DOWN DOWN - 180 DEGREE TURN OR "ABOUT FACE"
L1 + UP - CLIMB
DPAD - MOVE
R1 + CIRCLE - PICK UP ITEM
R1 + SQUARE - USE OR EAT ITEM
R1 + TRI - THROW ITEM
R1 + X - DROP ITEM
R1 + CIRCLE (WHILE HOLDING AN ITEM) - PUT ITEM IN BACKPACK (PLAYER CAN HOLD
UP TO 8 ITEMS)
SELECT + CIRCLE - OPENS WINDOWS
SELECT + X - CLOSES WINDOWS
L2 - TURNS ON OR OFF "ON-LINE" MANUAL

